description: You raise your e-cat living in Alexa with 'Cat Raiser'. You can feed it, pet it and frighten it. Your cat will purr to you if it feels happy! However, if you leave it along for a while, it will escape. So feed it everyday and listen how it feels!.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask cat raiser how is my cat
Alexa, ask cat raiser to feed my cat some fish
Alexa, launch cat raiser and pet its belly
name: Cat Raiser
shortDescription: Raise your e-cat living in Alexa!
